        <h2>Selected Law Firms</h2>
        <p>Dr. Lavian has worked with leading law firms across the United States and Canada on complex intellectual property litigation matters. His experience includes collaboration with prominent firms specializing in patent litigation, telecommunications law, and technology disputes.</p>
