        <h2>Expert Testimony and Litigation Support Services</h2>
        <p>Dr. Lavian provides expert testimony and litigation support services, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Testifying as an expert in cases filed with the United States District Court, the USPTO, the ITC, and other courts in the US and Canada.</li>
          <li>Serving as an expert witness in USPTO PTAB proceedings, including IPRs, CBM reviews, PGRs, Ex-Parte Re-Examinations, and PTO Interferences.</li>
          <li>Providing technical education for claim constructions and Markman hearings.</li>
          <li>Writing expert reports, including analyses, claim term definitions, and claim construction.</li>
          <li>Communicating technical information effectively to audiences of varying levels of technical expertise.</li>
          <li>Providing product and technical analyses related to patent portfolios, claim charts, prior art investigation, and patentability research.</li>
        </ul>

