        <h2>Expert Services</h2>
        <p>Dr. Lavian's expert services extend beyond simple technical analysis. He works closely with legal teams to understand the specific claims at issue, the relevant prior art, and the technical context of the litigation. His approach combines rigorous technical analysis with clear communication of complex concepts, ensuring that judges, juries, and hearing officers can comprehend the technical nuances central to the case.</p>

        <p>Whether preparing expert reports, testifying at depositions or trial, or providing Markman hearing support, Dr. Lavian brings years of experience and deep technical knowledge to every engagement. He understands the intersection of technology and patent law, and how to present technical information in a manner that directly addresses the claims and issues in dispute.</p>

        <p>His interdisciplinary background in academia and industry, combined with his publication record and patent portfolio, provides the foundation for credible and persuasive expert witness work. Dr. Lavian is committed to providing accurate, unbiased, and thorough technical analysis to support IP litigation.</p>

        <h2>Telecommunications and Network Communications Expertise</h2>
        <p>Dr. Lavian's specialized expertise spans across numerous telecommunications and network communications domains. The following areas represent key specializations where he has provided expert witness services:</p>

