          <h3 style="margin:0 0 8px 0;"><a href="/communications-expert-witness/telecommunications-expert-witness" style="color:#2d3e6f;text-decoration:none;">Telecommunications Expert Witness</a></h3>
          <p style="margin:0;color:#555;">Dr. Lavian provides expert witness services in patent cases involving telecommunications systems, architectures, and protocols. His expertise encompasses traditional PSTN systems, modern IP-based telecommunications, and the transition between legacy and next-generation telecom technologies. He has analyzed patents related to telephone systems, switching technologies, signaling protocols, and telecommunications network management.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="border-left:4px solid #2d3e6f;padding:16px 20px;margin:16px 0;background:#f8fafc;">
          <h3 style="margin:0 0 8px 0;"><a href="/communications-expert-witness/network-communications-expert-witness" style="color:#2d3e6f;text-decoration:none;">Network Communications Expert Witness</a></h3>
          <p style="margin:0;color:#555;">With deep expertise in network communications architectures and protocols, Dr. Lavian provides expert analysis on complex network systems. His knowledge covers OSI model layers, protocol stacks, interoperability challenges, and network optimization techniques. He has supported litigation involving network communication patents across multiple technology domains and vendor platforms.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="border-left:4px solid #2d3e6f;padding:16px 20px;margin:16px 0;background:#f8fafc;">
          <h3 style="margin:0 0 8px 0;"><a href="/communications-expert-witness/computer-networking-expert-witness" style="color:#2d3e6f;text-decoration:none;">Computer Networks Expert Witness</a></h3>
          <p style="margin:0;color:#555;">Dr. Lavian specializes in expert witness services for patent disputes involving computer networking technologies and systems. His expertise includes network design, topology, performance optimization, and network management. He has analyzed patents related to network architectures, network protocols, network security, and enterprise network systems.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="border-left:4px solid #2d3e6f;padding:16px 20px;margin:16px 0;background:#f8fafc;">
          <h3 style="margin:0 0 8px 0;"><a href="/communications-expert-witness/internet-expert-witness" style="color:#2d3e6f;text-decoration:none;">Internet Protocols Expert Witness</a></h3>
          <p style="margin:0;color:#555;">With extensive knowledge of Internet protocols and standards, Dr. Lavian provides expert analysis on patent disputes involving TCP/IP, UDP, and other core Internet protocols. His expertise extends to protocol implementation, interoperability, and the technical standards that govern Internet communications. He has supported litigation involving fundamental Internet technologies and their applications.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="border-left:4px solid #2d3e6f;padding:16px 20px;margin:16px 0;background:#f8fafc;">
          <h3 style="margin:0 0 8px 0;"><a href="/communications-expert-witness/internet-expert-witness" style="color:#2d3e6f;text-decoration:none;">Internet and Web Expert Witness</a></h3>
          <p style="margin:0;color:#555;">Dr. Lavian provides expert witness services for patent cases involving Internet and web technologies. His expertise encompasses web services, HTTP, DNS, web applications, and Internet-based systems. He has analyzed patents related to online services, e-commerce, web delivery technologies, and Internet infrastructure.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="border-left:4px solid #2d3e6f;padding:16px 20px;margin:16px 0;background:#f8fafc;">
          <h3 style="margin:0 0 8px 0;"><a href="/communications-expert-witness/routing-switching-expert" style="color:#2d3e6f;text-decoration:none;">Routing and Switching Expert Witness</a></h3>
          <p style="margin:0;color:#555;">With specialized expertise in network routing and switching technologies, Dr. Lavian provides expert analysis on patent disputes involving routers, switches, and packet forwarding systems. His knowledge covers routing protocols, switching architectures, network fabric design, and multi-protocol routing. He has supported cases involving major networking equipment manufacturers.</p>
        </div>

