          <h3 style="margin:0 0 8px 0;"><a href="/communications-expert-witness/voice-over-ip-voip-expert" style="color:#2d3e6f;text-decoration:none;">Voice Over IP (VoIP) Expert Witness</a></h3>
          <p style="margin:0;color:#555;">Dr. Lavian specializes in expert witness services for patent cases involving VoIP technologies and systems. His expertise includes VoIP protocols, voice codecs, quality of service, signaling mechanisms, and VoIP infrastructure. He has analyzed patents related to Internet telephony, unified communications, and voice transmission over IP networks.</p>
