          <p style="margin:0;color:#555;">With comprehensive expertise in mobile wireless technologies, Dr. Lavian provides expert analysis on patent disputes involving cellular systems, wireless protocols, and mobile network architectures. His knowledge covers cellular standards, wireless spectrum, mobile device communication, and wireless network optimization.</p>
