          <h3 style="margin:0 0 8px 0;"><a href="/communications-expert-witness/internet-expert-witness" style="color:#2d3e6f;text-decoration:none;">Web Technologies and Applications Expert Witness</a></h3>
          <p style="margin:0;color:#555;">With specialized expertise in web technologies and applications, Dr. Lavian provides expert witness services for patent cases involving web-based systems and services. His knowledge covers web frameworks, web protocols, web application architecture, and Internet-scale services. He has analyzed patents related to web technologies, online platforms, and Internet applications.</p>
